Model.Name: River_2
Model.Desc: Model for a bulk water unit with a variable volume

Param.Name: T_conv
Param.Desc: Time conversion factor from days to second

Param.Name: slp
Param.Desc: Average channel slope along channel length

Param.Name: W_b
Param.Desc: Width of channel at bottom of bank

Param.Name: Vol_init
Param.Desc: Initial volume of water as ratio on minimum

Param.Name: KO2
Param.Desc: Monod constant O2 on BOD decay

Param.Name: KSO2
Param.Desc: Monod constant O2 on sediment oxygen demand

AlgVar.Name: FluxPerComponent
AlgVar.Desc: Vector containing fluxes for all the components, the sum of all incoming and outgoing fluxes

AlgVar.Name: InFluxPerComponent
AlgVar.Desc: Vector containing incoming fluxes for all the components

AlgVar.Name: ConversionTermPerComponent
AlgVar.Desc: Vector containing conversionterms for all the components

AlgVar.Name: C
AlgVar.Desc: Vector containing concentrations for all the components

AlgVar.Name: A_man
AlgVar.Desc: Cross-sectional area bulk water tank, reduced fr Manning equation, due to d_min

AlgVar.Name: KL20
AlgVar.Desc: mass transfer at 20oC calculated form velocity and depth

DerVar.Name: M
DerVar.Desc: Vector containing masses for all the components
